title: More than 800 injured in clashes during Catalan independence vote
description:
More than 800 people were injured in clashes with police on Oct. 1 in the Catalonia region in northeast Spain during a vote on independence that the Spanish central government has called illegal. Subscribe to The Washington Post on YouTube: http://bit.ly/2qiJ4dy
